created_at.description:
A timestamp that marks when a user was deleted. It is in the format
yyyy-mm-ddThh:mm:ss.SZ. The timezone will always be UTC.

signed_token.description: This will be set only when an AccessToken is initially created

mappings.name: Lists Access Tokens that are configured for the authenticated user.
Returns the user object for the account authorized and making this request.

deleted_at.description:
A timestamp that marks when a user was deleted. It is in the format
yyyy-mm-ddThh:mm:ss.SZ. The timezone will always be UTC.
